article.title: The complex Monge-Ampère equation on weakly pseudoconvex domains

multiple_choice_question.text: What does the formula (ddu)^n = ψdV represent in the context of the complex Monge-Ampère equation?
choices: The Laplacian of the solution u
The complex Hessian of the solution u
The gradient of the solution u
The real Hessian of the solution u
